params.signatures: Proofs that orders have been created by makers.
params.takerAssetFillAmounts: Array of desired amounts of takerAsset to sell in orders.

cancelOrder((address,address,address,add.details: After calling, the order can not be filled anymore.      Throws if order is invalid or sender does not have permission to cancel.

params.order: Order to cancel. Order must be OrderStatus.FILLABLE.

cancelOrdersUpTo(uint256).details: Cancels all orders created by makerAddress with a salt less than or equal to the targetOrderEpoch      and senderAddress equal to msg.sender (or null address if msg.sender == makerAddress).

params.targetOrderEpoch: Orders created with a salt less or equal to this value will be cancelled.

executeTransaction(uint256,address,bytes.details: Executes an exchange method call in the context of signer.

params.salt: Arbitrary number to ensure uniqueness of transaction hash.
params.signature: Proof of signer transaction by signer.

fillOrKillOrder((address,address,address.details: Fills the input order. Reverts if exact takerAssetFillAmount not filled.

params.signature: Proof that order has been created by maker.
params.takerAssetFillAmount: Desired amount of takerAsset to sell.

params.signature: Proof that order has been created by maker.
params.takerAssetFillAmount: Desired amount of takerAsset to sell.

fillOrder((address,address,address,addre.return: Amounts filled and fees paid by maker and taker.

fillOrderNoThrow((address,address,addres.details: Fills the input order.      Returns false if the transaction would otherwise revert.

params.signature: Proof that order has been created by maker.
params.takerAssetFillAmount: Desired amount of takerAsset to sell.

fillOrderNoThrow((address,address,addres.return: Amounts filled and fees paid by maker and taker.

getAssetProxy(bytes4).return: The asset proxy registered to assetProxyId. Returns 0x0 if no proxy is registered.

getOrderInfo((address,address,address,ad.details: Gets information about an order: status, hash, and amount filled.

getOrdersInfo((address,address,address,a.details: Fetches information for all passed in orders.
getOrdersInfo((address,address,address,a.return: Array of OrderInfo instances that correspond to each order.

isValidSignature(bytes32,address,bytes).details: Verifies that a hash has been signed by the given signer.

params.signature: Proof that the hash has been signed by signer.
params.signerAddress: Address that should have signed the given hash.

isValidSignature(bytes32,address,bytes).return: True if the address recovered from the provided signature matches the input signer address.

marketBuyOrders((address,address,address.details: Synchronously executes multiple calls of fillOrder until total amount of makerAsset is bought by taker.

params.makerAssetFillAmount: Desired amount of makerAsset to buy.
params.signatures: Proofs that orders have been signed by makers.

marketBuyOrders((address,address,address.return: Amounts filled and fees paid by makers and taker.

marketBuyOrdersNoThrow((address,address,.details: Synchronously executes multiple fill orders in a single transaction until total amount is bought by taker.      Returns false if the transaction would otherwise revert.

params.signatures: Proofs that orders have been signed by makers.

marketBuyOrdersNoThrow((address,address,.return: Amounts filled and fees paid by makers and taker.

marketSellOrders((address,address,addres.return: Amounts filled and fees paid by makers and taker.

params.takerAssetFillAmount: Desired amount of takerAsset to sell.

marketSellOrdersNoThrow((address,address.return: Amounts filled and fees paid by makers and taker.

matchOrders((address,address,address,add.details: Match two complementary orders that have a profitable spread.      Each order is filled at their respective price point. However, the calculations are      carried out as though the orders are both being filled at the right order's price point.      The profit made by the left order goes to the taker (who matched the two orders).

params.leftSignature: Proof that order was created by the left maker.
params.rightSignature: Proof that order was created by the right maker.

matchOrders((address,address,address,add.return: matchedFillResults Amounts filled and fees paid by maker and taker of matched orders.

params.signerAddress: Address that should have signed the given hash.

params.assetProxy: Address of new asset proxy to register.
